atmPortCDVT.description: Cell Delay Variation Tolerance (CDVT) is measured in units of seconds per cell. For OC12c ATM the link rate is approximately 1.4 million cells per second, each cell time being approximately 700 nanoseconds. Its value is initialized to 50,000 which is approximately 0.7% of the OC12c line rate. The value ranges from 5,000 to 100,000 which gives us a CDVT range of 7 to 141 cell times.
